rows.label: qst103604_msg0001
rows.name:
We need to get out of this
town as soon as we can...

rows.label: qst103604_msg0005
rows.name:
May I ask to where you are
heading, from Nefer's fair city?

rows.label: qst103604_msg0006
rows.name:
Th-the Empire's most powerful
Blade?! Why are you here?!

rows.label: qst103604_msg0007
rows.name:
So you were followed, were
you...? Of all the careless...

rows.label: qst103604_msg0009
rows.name:
Well, we've got a chance
to strike a blow against
the Empire! Let's take it!
